    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push &amp; Plunder is a <strong>Miniature</strong> <strong>Action-Packed Arcade Wave Survival</strong> game where <strong>every shot counts!</strong> Harness physics-based coin shots to decimate the mighty bauble horde in chaotic, chain-reaction combat. Upgrade your abilities, unlock permanent power-ups, and create powerful builds to overcome waves of increasingly challenging enemies. Can you survive and bring an end to the bauble uprising?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111550/extras/c282bc99a8fc582ac1907e6cdba3a4f1.poster.avif?t=1769118940\" width=512 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111550/extras/c282bc99a8fc582ac1907e6cdba3a4f1.webm?t=1769118940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111550/extras/c282bc99a8fc582ac1907e6cdba3a4f1.mp4?t=1769118940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runs that last 10-30 minutes (depending on how well you did!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 90 Challenges to complete that reward you with...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlockable perks, equipment, and classes! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create unique Builds every run! </p></li></ul>",
